<br>
Now I just set up /trader and go to bed, wake up and see how many items I sold.<br>
<br>
It's also great for finding items with more people in the same zone selling items (and the same items) it makes people lower their prices to sell them half the time. So if I want to look for a item, it's not 5 items for the same price, they'll be like 2k, 1.8k 1.7k etc etc.<br>
<br>
If I'm going to be selling items I do the same thing, I'll search for who's selling the same thing and list my item at a decent / lowest price of the same item around.<br>
